sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Notebook as Notebook Controller

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: User Authentication and Dashboard Access
    User->>Router: GET / (initial request)
    Router->>Proxy: HTTPS/8443 (TLS Reencrypt)
    Proxy->>OAuth: OAuth redirect (no token)
    OAuth->>User: Login page
    User->>OAuth: POST credentials
    OAuth->>User: OAuth token (redirect)
    User->>Proxy: GET / with Bearer Token
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>ServiceAccount validation
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Token valid
    Proxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header
    Backend-->>Proxy: Dashboard HTML/JS
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS/8443 Dashboard

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: Create Jupyter Notebook
    User->>Proxy: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Impersonation headers
    Backend->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CRD<br/>ServiceAccount Token + Impersonation
    K8sAPI->>Notebook: Create Notebook resource
    Notebook->>K8sAPI: Create Pod
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook created
    Backend-->>User: 201 Created

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 3: WebSocket Resource Watch
    User->>Proxy: WebSocket /wss/k8s/notebooks<br/>wss:// Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: WebSocket /wss/k8s/notebooks<br/>ws:// Impersonation
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CRD<br/>wss:// ServiceAccount Token
    loop Real-time updates
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook status change
        Backend-->>User: WebSocket message
    end

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Query
    User->>Proxy: POST /api/prometheus<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080 Impersonation
    Backend->>Prometheus: POST /api/v1/query<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Prometheus-->>Backend: Metrics data (JSON)
    Backend-->>User: Metrics visualization
